-- Speed > 380 m/s (excitement)
-- Speed < 25 m/s (impatience)
-- Hull damage > 15 (alarm)
-- Hull critical (panic)
-- Tether hit / snap
-- Module unbolted
-- NLP exploit found
-- Slingshot achieved
-- Barge nearby
-- Fuel canister grabbed
